CORRECTED
1 F. The Commission shall also consider rules which may permit a
2 natural gas utility to begin to recover return on or return of
3 Construction-Work-In-Progress expenses prior to commercial operation
4 of a newly constructed energy infrastructure facility.
5 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
